name: Cycles
description: A cycles token by Dank that allows users & developers to hold cycles and develop with them with just a Principal ID. No need for a Cycles Wallet.

name: WICP
description: Wrapped version of the Internet Computer’s native ICP token that can be held by Principal IDs.

name: OGY
description: ORIGYN is a Swiss Nonprofit Foundation. At ORIGYN Foundation, we combine intelligent technologies and decentralized computing to identify, authenticate and unlock the powers of ownership for the world’s most valuable objects. ORIGYN brings NFTs to life with biometric data and unique ownership experiences to power brands, creators, artists, marketplaces, consumers and industries with guaranteed certificates of authenticity.
